<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1312998-received-an-email-today-from-the-author">Received an email today from the author saying it was free on Amazon for Kindle. This is free if you have Kindle Unlimited which has a membership fee. I have a Nook not a Kindle so I don&#39;t have Kindle Unlimited. It isn&#39;t on my Nook and I have senior eyes that can&#39;t read paperbacks anymore. It is not available at my library. Bummed as I would love to read it. Why isn&#39;t it available for my Nook?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
